r_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only that a month before he ruptured his Achilles tendon and goodbye to dreams of glory.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles\", \"score\": 0.9999997878835755, \"rank\": 2.121164516652547e-07, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He needed treatment, rehabilitation and then to cultivate that goal again, with ferocious dedication.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But how interminable can four years be.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He spends them all training for that handful of moments.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His journey is well worth a few handfuls of yawns.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also because if there is a specialty in which Italy can do well and an athlete reassures us, that is Jury.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2085087412389472e-13, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, while thousands of Italians dip biscuits or brioches in cups filled with milk or coffee, Chechi heads to the platform, toCentennial Olympic Park.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1464, \"end\": 1472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italians\", \"score\": 0.9529354303814218, \"rank\": 0.04938904370415973, \"text\": \"Italians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italians\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechi_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7523610626005415, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chechi\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechi_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechi_(film)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The audience is in liturgical silence, even from the kitchens and living rooms of the house.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He peers at the two rings to which he will have to cling: even though he is just over 160 centimeters tall, he is now called to climb to the top.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kneaded hands.\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Straight hair and blue vest.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Propitiatory puff.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an execution of less than a minute, the sacrifice of years is condensed.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jury knows it and stands up determined.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From there begins a clean sequence, free from smudges, the muscles tense, the gaze fiercely concentrated.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The people in the stands break that wall of silence only to applaud the perfect figures that Chechi manages to draw with his pirouettes.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechi_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7523610626005415, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chechi\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechi_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechi_(film)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then everyone holds their breath for that \\\"cross\\\" absolutely clear, terrifying and yet perfect: theLord of the Ringshe performs it almost effortlessly, without betraying the slightest hesitation.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Until that safe landing, the eyes finally shining with satisfaction, the lips widening in a smile.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the Rai commentator lets himself go to an uncontrollable exultation:\\\"There can be no doubt about it, this is a gold exercise!\\\".\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just enough time to wait for the jury's verdict, which will result ina gigantic 9,887.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All true.\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medal for Jury and for Italy, the first in gymnastics after the one won by Franco Menichelli in Tokyo, in 1964.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2811, \"end\": 2816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2085087412389472e-13, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 2831, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9987290517191904, \"rank\": 0.001272565644886497, \"text\": \"gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisco_Franco\", \"score\": 0.9947746443135467, \"rank\": 0.005244960516403961, \"text\": \"Franco\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisco_Franco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisco_Franco\"}, {\"begin\": 2884, \"end\": 2889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\"